        PartialDerivative(A(i), C(k), D(m))*B(j) \
        + PartialDerivative(A(i), C(k))*PartialDerivative(B(j), D(m))\
        + PartialDerivative(A(i), D(m))*PartialDerivative(B(j), C(k))\
        + A(i)*PartialDerivative(B(j), C(k), D(m))


